<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover">
<title>九年级上册 · 核心词汇 全册音频</title>
<style>
  :root{--navy:#102a54;--gold:#b8902f;--ink:#26303f;--bg:#f6f2e9;--card:#fff;}
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);
    font-family:-apple-system,"PingFang SC","Noto Sans SC",Inter,system-ui,sans-serif;
    -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;}
  .wrap{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:22px 16px 56px;}
  header{text-align:center;padding:14px 0 6px;}
  .kicker{color:var(--gold);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.22em;font-size:12px;}
  h1{margin:.32em 0 .12em;color:var(--navy);font-size:23px;letter-spacing:.02em;}
  .lead{color:#6b7480;font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;margin:.2em 0 0;}
  .rule{height:2px;width:54px;background:var(--gold);margin:14px auto 4px;border-radius:2px;}
  .card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid #e8e0cf;border-radius:14px;
    padding:15px 16px 17px;margin:15px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 14px rgba(16,42,84,.05);}
  .uhead{display:flex;align-items:baseline;justify-content:space-between;
    border-bottom:1px solid #efe7d6;padding-bottom:9px;margin-bottom:11px;}
  .unum{color:var(--navy);font-weight:800;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:.08em;}
  .wc{color:var(--gold);font-weight:700;font-size:13px;}
  .track{margin:11px 0;}
  .tlabel{font-size:14px;font-weight:650;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:7px;}
  .tlabel .sub{display:block;font-weight:400;color:#8a929c;font-size:12px;margin-top:2px;}
  audio{width:100%;height:38px;}
  footer{text-align:center;color:#9aa1ab;font-size:12px;margin-top:26px;line-height:1.7;}
</style></head>
<body><div class="wrap">
  <header>
    <div class="kicker">人教版 · 2026 秋新教材</div>
    <h1>九年级上册 · 核心词汇 全册音频</h1>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <p class="lead">英音朗读（en-GB）· 慢速精读 + 常速跟读 + 听默自测<br>共 8 单元 · 485 词 · 扫码即听</p>
